---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/5 via-transparent to-purple-500/5"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-50"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-500/8 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center reveal">
    <div class="card-base p-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-surface-800/80 to-surface-800/40 border-surface-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm">

      <div class="text-5xl mb-6 animate-float">🧬</div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-2">
        <span class="lang-zh">蒸馏了什么好东西？<br/><span class="gradient-text">分享出来啊！</span></span>
        <span class="lang-en">Distilled something great?<br/><span class="gradient-text">Share it with the world.</span></span>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-surface-400 text-lg mb-2 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <span class="lang-zh">你蒸馏的那个人，可能正是别人找了很久的。</span>
        <span class="lang-en">The person you distilled might be exactly who someone else has been looking for.</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-surface-500 text-sm mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        <span class="lang-zh">大牛、导师、某本书的作者、某个领域的专家——<br/>提交到 Gallery，让更多人用上。</span>
        <span class="lang-en">A brilliant engineer, a legendary mentor, a book author, a domain expert —<br/>submit to the Gallery and let the world summon them too.</span>
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-10">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/titanwings/colleague-skill-site/issues/new?template=submit-skill.yml"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-primary text-base px-8 py-4"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="lang-zh">提交我的 Skill</span>
          <span class="lang-en">Submit My Skill</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href={`${base}/gallery/`}
          class="btn-secondary text-base px-8 py-4"
        >
          <span class="lang-zh">先逛逛 Gallery →</span>
          <span class="lang-en">Browse Gallery →</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-10 gap-y-4 pt-8 border-t border-surface-700/50">
        {[
          { numZh: '2 分钟', numEn: '2 min', labelZh: '填一个 Issue 表单', labelEn: 'Fill an Issue form' },
          { numZh: '自动', numEn: 'Auto', labelZh: 'CI 校验格式', labelEn: 'CI validates format' },
          { numZh: '合并后', numEn: 'On merge', labelZh: '立即出现在 Gallery', labelEn: 'Instantly live in Gallery' },
        ].map((s) => (
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-brand-400 font-bold text-lg">
              <span class="lang-zh">{s.numZh}</span>
              <span class="lang-en">{s.numEn}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-surface-500 text-sm mt-0.5">
              <span class="lang-zh">{s.labelZh}</span>
              <span class="lang-en">{s.labelEn}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
